</div><script>
    (function() {
        const ul = document.getElementById('face-shapes');
        const faceItems = ul.children;
        const facesPerSlide = 15;
        const total = faceItems.length;
        const maxSlide = Math.ceil(total / facesPerSlide) - 1;
        let slide = 0;
        const indicator = document.getElementById('face-slider-indicator');
        function updateIndicator() {
            indicator.textContent = `${slide + 1} / ${maxSlide + 1}`;
        }
        updateIndicator();



        // Wrap each group of 10 faces into a slide
        const slides = [];
        for (let i = 0; i <= maxSlide; i++) {
            const slideEl = document.createElement('ul');
            slideEl.className = 'options spg-slider-target';
            slideEl.style.display = 'grid';
            slideEl.style.gridTemplateColumns = 'repeat(5, 60px)';
            slideEl.style.gridTemplateRows = 'repeat(3, 60px)';
            slideEl.style.gap = '14px 30px';
            slideEl.style.position = 'absolute';
            slideEl.style.top = '0';
            slideEl.style.left = '0';
            slideEl.style.transition = 'opacity 0.3s';
            slideEl.style.opacity = '0';
            slideEl.style.pointerEvents = 'none';

            for (let j = i * facesPerSlide; j < (i + 1) * facesPerSlide && j < total; j++) {
                slideEl.appendChild(faceItems[0]);
                // move <li> into slide
            }

            ul.parentElement.appendChild(slideEl);
            slides.push(slideEl);
        }

        // Hide original UL
        ul.remove();

        function updateSlider() {
            slides.forEach( (s, i) => {
                if (i === slide) {
                    s.style.opacity = '1';
                    s.style.pointerEvents = 'auto';
                    s.style.zIndex = '1';
                } else {
                    s.style.opacity = '0';
                    s.style.pointerEvents = 'none';
                    s.style.zIndex = '0';
                }
            }
            );

            document.getElementById('face-slider-prev').disabled = slide === 0;
            document.getElementById('face-slider-next').disabled = slide === maxSlide;
        }

        document.getElementById('face-slider-prev').onclick = function() {
            if (slide > 0) {
                slide--;
                updateSlider();
                updateIndicator();

            }
        }
        ;
        document.getElementById('face-slider-next').onclick = function() {
            if (slide < maxSlide) {
                slide++;
                updateSlider();
                updateIndicator();
            }
        }
        updateSlider();
        updateIndicator();
    }
    )();


</script>

    // Hide popup

    }

    document.getElementById('custom-popup-bg').onclick = function() {
        document.getElementById('custom-popup-bg').style.display = 'none';
        document.getElementById('custom-popup').style.display = 'none';
    }
    ;

    // Handle part link clicks
    document.querySelectorAll('#custom-part-list a').forEach(function(link) {
        link.onclick = function(e) {
            e.preventDefault();
            var part = this.getAttribute('data-part');
            // Hide all shapeSelector sections
            document.querySelectorAll('#shapeSelectorContainer .shapeSelector').forEach(function(sec) {
                sec.style.display = 'none';
            });
            // Show the selected part section
            var target = document.querySelector('#shapeSelectorContainer .shapeSelector[data-part="' + part + '"]');
            if (target)
                target.style.display = 'block';
            // Close the popup
            document.getElementById('custom-popup-bg').style.display = 'none';
            document.getElementById('custom-popup').style.display = 'none';
        }
        ;
    });

    // Simple slider logic for face shapes
    (function() {
        var ul = document.getElementById('face-shapes');
        var liWidth = 64;
        // 56px img + 8px margin
        var visibleCount = 5;
        var position = 0;
        var total = ul.children.length;

        function updateSlider() {
            ul.style.left = (-position * liWidth) + 'px';
            document.getElementById('face-slider-prev').disabled = position === 0;
            document.getElementById('face-slider-next').disabled = position >= total - visibleCount;
        }

        document.getElementById('face-slider-prev').onclick = function() {
            if (position > 0) {
                position--;
                updateSlider();
            }
        }
        ;
        document.getElementById('face-slider-next').onclick = function() {
            if (position < total - visibleCount) {
                position++;
                updateSlider();
            }
        }
        ;
        updateSlider();
    }
    )();
</script>
